OL,3,CRob Burrow's wife Lindsey describes
OL,4,Chis final moments 'surrounded by love'
OL,6,FRob Burrow's wife Lindsey has opened
OL,7,Fup about his final moments, saying he
OL,8,Fdied "surrounded by love".
OL,10,FTh ex-Leeds Rhinos star lost his life
OL,11,Fin June 2024 at the age of 41 after
OL,12,Fbeing diagnosed with motor neurone
OL,13,Fdisease (MND) in December 2019.
OL,15,FLindsey told ITV News she could "never
OL,16,Fprepare myself" for his death.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/13
