OL,3,CRob Burrow's wife Lindsey describes
OL,4,Chis final moments 'surrounded by love'
OL,6,F"But I took real strength and comfort
OL,7,Fin the thought that Rob had had
OL,8,Fenough, he'd fought his battle and we
OL,9,Fwere all there. He was surrounded by
OL,10,Fhis family, by the ones who love him
OL,11,Fthe most, and he went really
OL,12,Fpeacefully, surrounded by love."
OL,14,FBurrow, who played almost 500 times
OL,15,Ffor Leeds Rhinos over a 16-year
OL,16,Fcareer, became a high-profile
OL,17,Fcampaigner for MND awareness and
OL,18,Fhelped to raise millions of pounds for
OL,19,Fresearch.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/13
