OL,3,CRob Burrow's wife Lindsey describes
OL,4,Chis final moments 'surrounded by love'
OL,6,FA specialist MND centre is being built
OL,7,Fin Leeds in his name.
OL,9,FLindsey has now written a memoir, Take
OL,10,FCare, about her time as her husband's
OL,11,Fcarer.
OL,13,FIn it she shares photographs of the
OL,14,Ffamily with Rob in his final moments.
OL,16,F"The children had big smiles on their
OL,17,Ffaces, painting his nails, making
OL,18,Fthose memories so I'm so grateful we
OL,19,Fhad that time as a family," she said.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/13
