OL,3,CRob Burrow's wife Lindsey describes
OL,4,Chis final moments 'surrounded by love'
OL,6,F"I hope that the children don't fear
OL,7,Fdeath because he went very peacefully
OL,8,Fand that's the best we could've asked.
OL,10,F"When you love somebody you don't want
OL,11,Fto see them suffering and at the end
OL,12,Fit was tough, Rob had fought his
OL,13,Fbattle. It was time."
OL,15,FLindsey said she was supported by the
OL,16,Fhospital staff and all those caring
OL,17,Ffor Rob in his final days.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/13
