OL,3,CRob Burrow's wife Lindsey describes
OL,4,Chis final moments 'surrounded by love'
OL,6,FShe added: "I had the support of the
OL,7,Fhospital staff who were brilliant and
OL,8,Fsaid 'you haven't done anything wrong,
OL,9,FRob isn't going to get better'. He was
OL,10,Freally tired and struggling.
OL,12,F"But you do question, should I have
OL,13,Fsaid 'do you want to keep fighting
OL,14,FRob, have you had enough?' So I did
OL,15,Fhaunt myself over that. But I think
OL,16,Fthe support of the hospital staff and
OL,17,Fthe family (helped) and Rob had
OL,18,Fcommunicated through his eyes that
OL,19,Fhe'd had enough and we had to respect
OL,20,FRob's wishes."
