OL,3,CRob Burrow's wife Lindsey describes
OL,4,Chis final moments 'surrounded by love'
OL,6,FIn the memoir, Lindsey details her
OL,7,Ftime juggling her work as a
OL,8,Fphysiotherapist for the NHS, being
OL,9,FRob's carer, and looking after her
OL,10,Fchildren.
OL,12,FShe said: "I wanted to write the book
OL,13,Fto shine a light on the work carers
OL,14,Fdo. Millions of carers do what I do
OL,15,Fday in day out and I just thought
OL,16,Fsharing my story of looking after work
OL,17,Fand juggling the work and children and
OL,18,Ffamily life can hopefully help another
OL,19,Fperson or another family.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/13
