OL,3,CRob Burrow's wife Lindsey describes
OL,4,Chis final moments 'surrounded by love'
OL,6,F"I wanted to be honest and open. I
OL,7,Fappreciate that I probably have set
OL,8,Fmyself up to be quite vulnerable but
OL,9,FRob was so honest, he showed people
OL,10,Fthe reality of living with MND.
OL,12,F"I had Rob's permission to do the
OL,13,Fbook, he actually encouraged me to do
OL,14,Fit. I just felt that I had to be
OL,15,Ftruthful because there will be other
OL,16,Fpeople who go through that situation.
OL,17,FIf reading my story helps them through
OL,18,Fthat then that's why I did it."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/13
