OL,3,CRob Burrow's wife Lindsey describes
OL,4,Chis final moments 'surrounded by love'
OL,6,F"I was just stood there and felt so
OL,7,Fmuch pride knowing this centre will be
OL,8,Fin Rob's name and help so many other
OL,9,Ffamilies that have been through or are
OL,10,Fgoing to go through a similar journey
OL,11,Fto what we've been on. Just having
OL,12,Fthat purpose built centre will make
OL,13,Fsuch a difference.
OL,15,F"Having it in Rob's name, a place I
OL,16,Fcan take the children and we can
OL,17,Fcelebrate Rob's life and legacy is
OL,18,Freally special.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G10/13
