OL,3,CRob Burrow's wife Lindsey describes
OL,4,Chis final moments 'surrounded by love'
OL,6,F"The MND community is not one you want
OL,7,Fto be a part of but actually once
OL,8,Fyou're in it the people you meet along
OL,9,Fthe way, they're the real heroes. I'm
OL,10,Fjust in complete awe of them.
OL,12,F"To go out and show the world about
OL,13,FMND and what it does to a person when
OL,14,Fhe's at his most vulnerable is such a
OL,15,Fcourageous and brave thing to do and
OL,16,FI'm so proud of rob for that.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G11/13
