OL,3,CRob Burrow's wife Lindsey describes
OL,4,Chis final moments 'surrounded by love'
OL,6,F"He wanted to help raise awareness for
OL,7,Fthe school teacher, the post man, the
OL,8,Fbricklayer. The people who dont have a
OL,9,Fvoice. And people now know what MND is
OL,10,Fand his legacy is one of hope and
OL,11,Finspiration."
OL,13,FLindsey said it had been a tough eight
OL,14,Fmonth since his death, but that she is
OL,15,Fkeeping positive - inspired by her
OL,16,Fhusband.
OL,18,FShe said: "I miss him so much every
OL,19,Fday but I still feel he's with us.
OL,20,FWhatever we do he'll always be with is.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G12/13
