OL,3,CRob Burrow's wife Lindsey describes
OL,4,Chis final moments 'surrounded by love'
OL,6,F"Rob showed us how to be brave, how to
OL,7,Fbe positive and ultimately that life
OL,8,Fis for living. He wanted us to be
OL,9,Fhappy and I promised him we would
OL,10,Fcontinue his legacy.
OL,12,F"There are tough times, there are
OL,13,Ftimes when you want to just pull the
OL,14,Fduvet over your head and go to sleep
OL,15,Fbut I feel so fortunate that I was
OL,16,FRob's wife for 17 years. I've got 3
OL,17,Fbeautiful children and that's my focus
OL,18,Fnow.
OL,20,F"My priority now is making sure they
OL,21,Fhave the best childhoods."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G13/13
